Dialogs.Dialog: Do you know that there are about 600 kinds of cherry blossoms？
Manaka
There are that many？
Yeah. There are also cherry blossoms that have yellow petals.
Yellow！？ Hmm... I thought that all cherry blossoms were pink.
...Hey, what if we make our goal to watch all kinds of cherry blossoms？
Haha. That will take such a long time.
You mean, like, forever？
I guess.
Hehe. Then let's make a promise to do so.
Manaka
It's hot today... Hey, shall we take some rest under that tree's shade？
In that case, wait for me on that bench. I'll be right back！
Eh？ Where are you going？
Just wait！
Welcome back... Eh？ Ice cream？
I dashed here so that it didn't melt. I saw that ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s face was quite pale.
And you bought only one？ Hehe, you're so hasty.
...Ah, t-then you eat this one first. I'll run back to get more...
Hey, why don't we share this one？ I'll go with you to buy more later.
...I won't allow you to leave me alone anymore.
Manaka
Amazing. Doesn't the lawn look like a yellow carpet？
Yeah, and the days are becoming shorter...
...After I met you, I started to like this season more and more.
Why？
I could feel the warmth of your hands.
After, I realized how much I didn't want to be away from you...
Sort of. Yeah... Let's pick some ginkgo leaves. We can press them to make some bookmarks.
Ah, so cold...
Manaka
It's cold because all of the leaves have fallen. This street feels so windy.
Ah, I see... Usually, the leaves block the wind for us. That makes sense.
Right... Hey, shall we go somewhere warmer？ It's getting very cold here.
...Hey. Why are you being stubborn like this？
Because you can get the warmth from me. Come on. Give me your hand.
...That's not enough.
Eh？
You will have to hug me tightly... If you do that, I'll stay here with you.
Manaka
Hey. Let's compete to see who can run up these stairs and reach the shrine first.
Good idea. Then the loser must follow whatever the winner says！
Hehe. You're fired up, huh？ How about you give me 50 steps as a handicap？
▲高嶺＊＊▲ is too good for a handicap like that. Even without a handicap, I'm still not sure I could win.
Hey, don't say it like that. You're getting much stronger lately.
I am？
Yeah, I can tell just by looking...
I shouldn't say that...
No, please feel free to watch me. I'll keep doing my best if I know that you are watching me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...Then I'll reduce the handicap to 30 steps. But I won't lose to you.
We're done with the shrine visit！ What did you wish for ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
It's a secret. You can't tell anyone what you wish for, you know？
You just wrote it on the wish board, right？ ...But I want to know.
...Don't make such a face.
Then give me some hints！
I wished you would never become any more handsome than this, ever.
Huh...？ That's your wish...？
If you become any more attractive, I'll feel insecure. I'm sorry that I wished for something so selfish...
I'll do my best to be suitable for you then.
Manaka
I visited this shrine a lot when I was a child...
Ah, I see. This place is spacious enough to be a good playground.
I liked to make flower crowns from this shrine's white clovers. I also searched for four-leaf clovers.
That's so girlish~.
Hehe, because I'm a girl. I also pretended to do things like exchanging rings and crowns.
Like a make-believe wedding ceremony？
Yeah.
I played with another girl, though.
I-I know that...
Haha！ Let's go. Maybe we can try acting that out too, all right？
Manaka
Hah...
Is there something wrong, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Why did you sigh like that？
The movie was wonderful. I long for a love like that.
The hero and the heroine had to go through many obstacles until they could be together. That part captivated me...
Hmm, but if we were them, I'm pretty sure we could also pass those obstacles.
Eh, am I wrong？
...No, I totally agree.
I was just surprised that you were thinking something like that...
Hehe. I'm happy.
Manaka
It was fun！
Yeah, it was great, especially the action scenes！
Yeah, it was amazing. If I could move my body like that, it would be so much fun.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you can move pretty well. You might be able to do something like that.
Hehe. You're pretty good yourself.
Nah...
Hey, how about we both aim to be action stars？
That sounds nice. In the end, we can become an action star couple.
Huh？
You... No, never mind.
Ah, it was interesting！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲, what do you think？
Manaka
Haha... Ahaha！
Sorry... But... Hahaha！
(So, ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s weak to those kinds of jokes？ Then...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲！ Here, look at my face！
！！ Kyaa...
How's this？
...Please... stop it... My stomach hurts... Hahaha！
(All right. I can use this move whenever she gets angry！)
Manaka
What's wrong？
Somehow, that movie was quite difficult to understand.
If you didn't watch the TV series, you probably wouldn't get it.
Did you watch it？
Yeah. Oh, shall I explain to you then？
Hmm... Then when the heroine acted like that...
Ah, that was because she could sense that the hero was in danger.
I see... If I knew this, it would've been easier to understand. I should've asked you beforehand.
You know a lot about this. If there's anything else I don't understand, can you explain it to me？
What an epic movie！
Manaka
...Hey, what does SF stand for？ Space Fantasy？
Huh？ Ah, it's Science Fiction.
Right！ I see... I was concerned about this the entire time I was watching the movie...
...Is that why you can't remember a lot about the movie？
...Sorry. At first, I was trying to keep myself awake, but I fell asleep halfway through.
But, the scene that the hero helped the heroine was wonderful, wasn't it？
(I guess Sci-Fi is not something she would enjoy...)
...▲高嶺＊＊▲. You look pale. Are you okay？
Manaka
I'm... not good with these kinds of movies...
Really？
I'm not quite afraid of ghosts or monsters, but...
...There was too much blood in this movie...
I see... Sorry.
No, you were holding my hand the whole time, right？ That's why I could watch it until the end.
You really did your best, huh？ But next time, don't overdo it, okay？
...Okay. Thanks.
Manaka
How are bowling scores calculated？
What do you mean？ They were calculated by the computer automatically.
I know. But it would be fun if I can calculate them myself too.
Well, that would be quite hectic, especially with things like Survival Bowling and such.
What is that？ Survival Bowling, you say？
In primitive bowling alleys, it was like a dog-eat-dog business...
"Throw it！ Throw it！" Something like that？
Yeah, like that.
Haha！ But, in case we encounter something like that, it'd be a good idea to learn how to count the scores.
Then, this time we'll count the score ourselves while we play.
You really know how to？ Wow！ Teacher, please teach me▼
Manaka
Why doesn't my score improve at all？
Hmm. It must be because of ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s form.
Really？ Where and how should I improve my form then？
How about you show me how you bowl？ I'll be watching carefully.
Watching me？
Yeah.
My form might be even weirder if you do that...
Why？
...Geez. Sometimes I wish I could also be this dumb.
Manaka
That throw just now was really nice...
Ah, the ball went really fast. I guess I did it well.
Hey, what should I do to be able to throw a ball with that much power？
If you gain more weight, you can throw it with more power！
Hmm... That's not quite sensible. How about something more logical...？
Instead of thinking of complicated ways, it's easier to keep playing until you get better.
...I see. That's right. All right！ We'll have to play 5 more games today.
Yeah！ ...What？ Five more！？
Manaka
Phew...
Tired？
No, I just got in the groove with the performance.
Ah, I understand. Musical shows are powerful for both the performers and the audience.
When you're spacing out, the performers will point at you and people will be staring at you.
Haha, you were stared.
At that time, I was too absorbed with the song.
Really？
Yeah, that song expressed intolerable feelings of lovers.
Wow... I didn't pay much attention to the lyrics. You were really attentive then.
(That's your response, huh, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...？)
Manaka
It was fun. There were many songs that I know.
Yeah！ Jazz sounds a little sophisticated for many people, but when you listen, that's what you feel.
When I talk about "modern jazz" or "swing jazz" to people, they usually say "Eh？" to me.
Hmm？ Did I say something weird？
No, Papa collects records so I've heard about those terms, but...
This is the first time I heard someone around my age mentioned "swing" and "modern."
Will you look at me differently from now on？
...No. On the contrary, I'm falling deeper in love with you now.
Manaka
The vocalist was amazing.
Yeah, to keep jumping around and singing out loud like that, it was amazing.
You're like that too, aren't you？ Whatever we do together, you never get tired before me.
For physical strength, you won't lose to that singer.
...What about everything else？
Hmm, what should I say？
Hehe！ Here's a hint. I only have one guy who is always my number one. Yeah...
(All right！ I should be proud of myself！)
Manaka
Shall I buy the CD...？
Oh, you really like it, huh？
Yeah. The last ballad was really wonderful.
Ah, it was good. The piano piece made me feel so sad. And that last song was very impressive.
...Hehe.
Hmm？
I was wondering if you'd like it. Now that I know, I'm very happy.
Hey, is it okay that we buy it and listen to it together？
Of course.
Hehe, I can't wait to listen to the CD.
Manaka
Hehe. It was fun！
Yeah, maybe I should try some gags like what they used in the show.
Hehe, like what？
Like... What do you call a rabbit with fleas？ ...Bugs Bunny！ ...How's that！？
(...W-Was it not funny at all...？)
Amazing！ Do you have any more jokes like that？ I want to hear more！
(She laughed... I'm glad ▲高嶺＊＊▲ enjoyed my joke...)
Manaka
Hey, about that leading actress...？
Ah, she's famous, right？ She stars in the morning drama series.
I see. That's why I thought she looked familiar.
By the way, the leading actor also stars in the same drama, as the main character's dad.
Ah！ Hey, did you watch it, too？
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you watched it, right？ I was imagining what kinds of TV shows you'd watch.
Your dad shouldn't have problem with you watching morning drama series, so I just tried watching it.
Why are you such a wonderful person？
...Hey, don't make me fall even deeper in love with you.
Manaka
Hmm？ What's wrong？
This ballad was so nice...
You're really good at sentimental songs, huh？ Especially the love songs.
That's because I was singing them with ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
！！ You're talking like this again...
I'm just telling you the truth.
...This is enough. Now, let's sing the next song！
(We've just finished one...)
Manaka
...Wonderful.
What is？
You sang that part without breathing at all. Your lungs must be big.
Well, if you practice, you can do that.
Is there anything else that you're good at...？
Anything else...？ Ah, I'm very confident with my all-night kara.
"All-night kara"？
"All night long karaoke." How's that？ Lady, will you take my challenge？ We can't sleep all night▼
I'm sorry. That's impossible... I usually fall asleep at 9 o'clock.
(She's taking it really seriously... And she sleeps at 9 o'clock？ Isn't that too early？)
Manaka
...Hey, can I ask you a question？
Hm？ What is it？
What is this button for？
Ah, if you push it, the machine will change your voice.
It's like a voice changer. My voice will become a female's voice, and ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s voice will be a male's voice.
Amazing...！
I should've asked you earlier. Hey, how about we sing a duet next？
Ah, I'm not sure if this function will work with duet songs.
Hey, then this button with hand icon will play clapping sounds, right？ Shall we try it？
(Haha. She's acting like a little kid.)
Manaka
Hey, what would you do if this Ferris wheel suddenly stopped？
Suddenly？
Yeah. And it would take a long time until help would come.
Well...
The first thing I'd do is hold you, I guess. Why, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I have to make you feel safe and secure, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. It's my first priority.
...Is it okay to say such cool things？ If it really happens, I'll expect it.
Absolutely okay. If anything happens, I will take care of you.
Then, shall I leave myself in your care？ ...Maybe.
Manaka
Why do all the Ferris wheels look the same？
Ah, maybe it would be nice if each of them looked different.
Like painting the outside of a car like a pumpkin carriage or something...
Ah, that would be wonderful.
And the interior should look better too. Maybe something like a princess castle.
Yeah yeah▼
Add drapes and some lacy curtains, and it would become ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s ideal Ferris wheel！
...You saw through me that much？ I regret it a bit now.
(I don't think you can hide that from me...)
Manaka
That ghost that came out last was really fast, right？
Yeah. We were running at full speed and it was still catching up with us.
I was thinking that I might fall down at any moment.
If you weren't holding my hand, it would've been quite dangerous.
Well, even if you did fall, you wouldn't need to worry.
Why？
In that case, I would've carried my princess ▲高嶺＊＊▲ in my arms and ran！
Haha. That's right. When that time comes, I'll put myself in your care▼
Manaka
If there were ghosts chasing after us in real life, that would be very scary.
In that case, we already have a powerful weapon against them.
...？ What kind of weapon？
The power of love！ Our love could knock out all the ghosts！
Hahaha. As if！
Huh？ What's wrong？
The way you were joking like that made me worry...
Please, I beg you. Don't ever flirt with any female ghosts, okay？
(How could I do that？ ...It's scary just to think about it！)
Manaka
Hah... It was great, right？
Yeah... Hey, was I being overly excited or something？
Eh？ No, I don't think so. You were just enjoying it like usual.
Really？ Why did I feel like you were staring at me the whole time...？ Probably just my imagination.
...Next time, I should try to enjoy the ride...
Huh？
That way, I won't pay as much attention to you.
Pay attention to me？
Yeah. Oh, geez. Don't you realize how attractive you are？
(I also want to say exactly the same thing to her...)
Manaka
Hehe！ Wasn't that last dip amazing？
Yeah. It was like "whoosh" and then it was "wheeez" all of a sudden.
Yeah. And after that it was like "gyooosh"！
Right！ And the best part was when it went "gyaaash." This roller coaster is just awesome.
...Haha！
What？
I wonder if anyone could understand what we were saying.
It sounds like we are an old married couple. This is wonderful. Hehe.
Oh, look, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. The princess is waving at us. Yay！
Manaka
What's wrong？
She winked at you, right？
Yeah, she did.
...She even threw a kiss at you.
That's just a fan service.
Ah, the prince is waving at me▼
What！？
It's just a fan service, right？ Hehe. I should wave back at him too.
(Urgh... I have to watch my speech and behavior...)
Manaka
Somehow, I feel like I am really in a fairyland.
This is just fantastic. Really...
Yes. I don't know why, but I also feel lonely...
...▲高嶺＊＊▲, give me your hand.
Eh？ ...Sure.
How do you feel now？
A little embarrassed, but I'm happy...
All right. We will stay like this today then.
...Okay. Don't ever let go of my hand, okay？
Manaka
Somehow, I feel like I am in a wonderland.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, if you were Alice, then I would be the rabbit.
Hehe！ And you would be my guide for the whole day. Thank you, Mr. Rabbit▼
Where would you take me next？
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I can take you to wherever you desire.
Then take a guess.
You want to be in my arms？ ...How's that？
Hey... Although it isn't correct, I'll make it a correct answer for you. Now, take me there, won't you？
Manaka
Phew...
Here, a towel. Wow, you were really great, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
What do you mean？
Your swimming form was so wonderful. You looked like a mermaid when you were in the pool.
Are you trying to flatter me again？
I mean it. Everyone was looking at you too.
...Then you, too.
Me？
...Hey. I won't let you be away from me today, okay？
(I feel so happy with this... Why？)
Manaka
It feels so strange to float quietly over the water. Don't you think so？
Feels strange？
Yeah. It feels like I'm dissolving.
There is a saying that humans come from the water. I can feel that now.
It's very relaxing. I think there's a type of therapy that uses this method, too.
Hmm？ Really？ That sounds nice.
There are too many people today, so we can't...
But some day, let's try to dissolve somewhere together.
Manaka
I'm really no match for a guy...
Huh？
We swam the same distance, but you didn't get tired at all.
If we had the same physical strength, I would be really shocked.
Yeah, I agree, but...
And I also have my other source of stamina.
Other source？
See？ If I see you in a swimsuit like this, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, I can never feel tired.
...Pervert！
The reflection of those falling stars was so beautiful...
Manaka
Yeah. The background music was amazing too, but we won't hear such music in reality.
Yeah, this was a show after all.
Right. Small kids could get the wrong idea about this.
In that case, it's our duty to teach them the right thing.
Huh？
No. I'm just thinking that you could be a very good father.
And then there will be... Hehehe！
(She's enjoying it... I wonder what she's picturing in her head.)
Manaka
The ancient people really had amazing imaginations. They connected these stars and pictured them as gods.
There must have been a lot more visible stars then.
Now, a lot of them can only be viewed at the planetarium.
Right... There are also stars that have already disappeared.
I used to think that it was mysterious how we still saw its light when the star itself already disappeared.
It has something to do with the speed of light, right？
Hehe. Hey, a lot of couples would have this kind of conversation, don't you think？
Yeah. I bet there are more than the number of the stars！
"And now, we will ask the next couple to speak up." Something like that？ Hehe.
I really lose track of time when I'm here.
Manaka
Yes, I also feel at ease here... It has relaxing atmosphere, I guess.
Probably. It's peaceful and has dim light... But the most relaxing thing is...
What is it？
▲高嶺＊＊▲'s hand. I felt so relaxed that I dozed off.
Actually, me too. Your hand was so warm that I couldn't help falling asleep.
Then we shouldn't hold hands next time.
Oh no！ We must keep holding hands. Do you understand？ What's your reply？
Yes！ I understand.
Hehe. Very well！
Manaka
If you could live in a place like this, you could get fresh air all the time...
Being with lots of plants like this is good for your health too.
Yeah, I wonder if it's practical.
Recent scientific research shows that this has some positive effects for your health.
Hmm... I think it's because you can feel relaxed here.
Isn't that right？ Here, you can do nothing, or sleep all day, or just space out like ▲高嶺＊＊▲ now.
Then... That's because of you.
Me？
The ways you act and talk make me feel relaxed.
Then, me too. Looking at ▲高嶺＊＊▲ makes me a little drowsy.
Hey, you're getting ahead of yourself again... Well, shall we rest for a bit？
Manaka
I wonder why carnivorous plants eat insects.
Due to the low-quality soil, they have to consume insects to get their nutrients.
See this huge fat pitcher plant？ If you grew it in nutritious soil, it wouldn't grow this big.
Hmm...
And in that case, the fluid it uses to dissolve insects would turn into water in the end.
You know a lot. Have you read books on this？
...Urgh. This is all written on that explanation board.
Eh？ When did you read it？
I read a little bit every time I visit here.
...Now I regret this. From now on, I'll read it when I come here as well.
(...Did I just set a fire？)
Manaka
Hmm？
I'm sorry. I fell asleep. Was I heavy？
Not at all. I even feel like you should gain more weight.
Hey. You're making fun of me again...
Ah, this shoulder of mine is getting cold now. It's crying that it's lonely~！
...Hehe. I have no choice. I'll lean on it then.
And this time, I'll stay like this and won't leave.
Manaka
...You fell asleep halfway, right？
Sorry. I was feeling really comfortable and when I realized it...
I know...
If it were an event where I could sleep peacefully like a classical concert, it would be nice.
Are those held here too？
I guess. Those kinds of concerts have very nice atmospheres.
I agree. Maybe we should come watch one...
But next time you come to watch something, please don't fall asleep.
...It would be bad if we couldn't talk about the event on our way home.
(Urgh！ I'll try...)
Manaka
There are so many fans.
This show is very popular. I often see it on TV.
Really？
Yeah. Only a few people in Japan wouldn't know about this.
...Hmm？
(Ah, no. If I say it like that...)
I'll have to buy some magazines before we head home.
Eh？
First, I have to start with information gathering. Yeah.
(Ah, as I thought...)
Manaka
The musical was amazing...
There were many songs that were so sudden, like the one right after Act II.
Right！ When they came out and walked right toward us with their smiling faces...
Looking at them singing with such faces, all of us in the audience couldn't help but smile with them.
Yeah, everyone around us was smiling.
But your smiling face is the loveliest one. You smiled with your eyes open widely.
Were you watching me...？
Hehe！ Are you getting shy？ You're just so cute▼
(This is embarrassing！)
Manaka
Hey, that technique that the winner used, what was it？
It's called Arm Crush Cross Lock. Are you interested in it？
Yeah, a little bit. That must have hurt really badly.
I think it's a very effective attack. It is originally from Judo.
I see. Do you know how to do that move？
Well... Hey, don't tell me you want to try it.
I wonder if you can withstand that attack. Hey, shall we try？
Eh！？ You mean try that attack！？
Of course. Just once, okay！？
(A-Are you serious！？)
Manaka
Hey, what are those things that people are holding？
Ah, those are cheering megaphones. The fans clap them together when they cheer for their teams.
That sounds fun...
Yeah, the drumming noises get people excited.
Next time, shall we join them？
...Yes！
All right. Then for the time being, we have to get our own megaphones first！
Okay, Commander！ Teehee▼
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Are you okay？ You look pale.
Manaka
It was too crowded...
This is bad... There's a bench over there. Do you think you can walk to that bench？
Yes...
Then let's go. Just move slowly, okay？
How is it？ Do you feel like you can walk now？
Yeah, I'm okay now... Sorry. We came all this way, but...
Don't worry. It was really crowded, so things like this couldn't be helped. Well, what do you say？
...Thank you.
You're welcome！
It looks totally different when the lights are on.
Manaka
Yeah, it's beautiful, and also...？
I'm so glad to have met you...
Otherwise, I would never be able to enjoy such scenery.
Thank you for being with me... Yeah...
There are still more.
Eh？
▲高嶺＊＊▲, there are still a lot more places that I want to see with you.
So, please accompany me to those places as well, okay？
...Of course！
Manaka
It's beautiful...
If I said that this was like heaven on earth, it'd probably be too cliched.
But I can't think of any expression that fits this scenery better.
Something that fits this scenery...？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Huh？
You are my shining star.
How does that sound？
...If you don't say this at night, it's rejected！
But that made me happy, so I'll let it pass. I hope I can be your star forever...
That was awesome. Those seagulls got really close to us. ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Why？ They only gathered around you.
I-I don't know...
It's not fair.
I can't do anything about that...
Not just girls... Even the birds, too！
T-That's beyond my control！
For the girls, too！？
That's a different story...
...Geez. I don't care anymore.
(Hah... What should I say in this situation！？)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you tired？
Manaka
Yeah... I was in high spirits all day. Now, I'm a bit sleepy.
You did put all your effort in swimming.
But, that was because you challenged me！
And you didn't go easy on me at all.
If I did, you would get mad.
Right. Hehe. You really know me well.
Because I'm your boyfriend. And I wanted to show you my strong points.
You have shown me your strong points. Because of that, now I'm so tired.
I'll take responsibility. I'll guard you, so please have a peaceful nap.
I think I'll accept your courtesy. I am in your care, my bodyguard▼
I'm getting hungry. We also ran out of drinking water. I'll buy some.
Manaka
Okay, hurry there and come back. I'll time it▼ Ready？ Go！
Hey, doing this all of a sudden is too sneaky！ Ah！ I'll be right back！
Welcome back. Wow, you set a new record！
I-I'm back... Here, your noodles and hotdogs... and some water.
Thanks▼ Ah, no chopsticks.
Really！？ Hah, do I have to run back there again...？
Ah, I'll go there. You rest here, okay？
All right... Ready？ Go！
Eh？ Are you going to time me？ Really？ That's unfair！
(She's running at full speed. ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is serious about this...)
Manaka
The reflection of the sunset on the sea is beautiful...
Yeah. I've never noticed before, but the sun is going down quite quickly.
Hehe, I know... Hey, do you see that rock over there？
Yeah. What's with it？
There's a rumor that if lovers watch sunset from that rock, they will be blessed with happiness.
Hmm？ We should go there the next time we have a chance.
Geez. I was about to say that.
Victory goes to the one who makes the first move. Oh, the sun has set pretty far already.
Yeah, today was really fun. Thank you.
Manaka
It feels nice to walk leisurely when no one else is on the beach.
Yeah, it's good for a change of mood.
Right, I used to come here often with Papa and Mama when I was a child.
Hmm？ How about now？
We do it occasionally. But my feelings have changed somehow.
In what way？
Now, I want them to have their time alone. In the past, I liked to be with them, but...
Now, I enjoy watching their backs while they are walking hand-in-hand and smiling.
After I met you, I've become more mature, I guess...
Manaka
The sound of the wind is scary...
During this season, the sounds of the waves get tenser too.
Yeah. At a time like this, I feel quite lonely...
It makes you think that the world might end one day, or something like that？
That's right. What if the world would end？ What would you do？
For me... I would want to be with my significant other.
I was thinking the same thing.
And could you be holding that person's hand right now？
Right. You know me well.
